        "@value": "A concept being an instance of PotentialConsequence is a suggestion that the concept can be a 'risk' within an use-case - this suggestion is not exclusive and the concept may also be instances of other potential concepts to indicate the multiple possible roles a concept can take. This suggestion can be ignored if it is not applicable to the use-case"
      }
    ]
  },
